=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex22 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 919 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: stable
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 918.9587
  harmonic_decay_rate: -15.9858
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5007
  pitch_clarity: 100.2020
  inharmonicity: 0.0024
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -3.9747
  resonance_freq: 925.9277

